{"word":"ἀναφύω","slug":"ἀναφύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναφύω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to produce again, to let grow</i>, <el>πώγωνα</el> <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, with aor2 <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>ἀν-έφυν</el>, <a href='S:perfect tense'>pf.</a> <el>ἀμ-πέφῡκα</el>, <i>to grow up</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to grow again</i>, of the hair, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}